snippet.title: My Van is Dead.
snippet.description:
Amber is not well.
Some things have been underlying for a while getting slowly worse, others have sprung out on me as a surprise. But now I have a lot of issues to contend with and a tough decision to make on the future of my van/home.

So of course, I chose the most ridiculous, outlandish choice available.


Subscribe to keep up with Project.Amber:
https://www.youtube.com/c/projectamber

Find most parts, items & accesories I've used in videos on my
Amazon Store:
https://www.amazon.co.uk/shop/projectamber
You can also follow on:
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/project.amber/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ProjectAmber25.Vanlife/

Want to help support the channel?:
Patreon: Project.Amber
https://www.patreon.com/Projectamber


#Couldbetheend #vanlifeuk #t1nSprinter
